stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> Buffering : sign_start
  Buffering --> Inferring : buffer >= 6 frames
  Inferring --> Buffering : confidence < threshold
  Inferring --> Voting : confidence >= threshold
  Voting --> Buffering : no 2/3 consensus
  Voting --> Cooldown : sign accepted (emit)
  Cooldown --> Buffering : cooldown elapsed (8 frames)
  Buffering --> Idle : hand gap > 3 frames (reset)
  Inferring --> Idle : sign_stop
  Buffering --> Idle : sign_stop
  Cooldown --> Idle : sign_stop
  Idle --> [*] : disconnect
